On Sat, Jan 26, 2008 at 04:43:43PM +0100, Richard Hartmann wrote:
> I forgot to ask what you meant by 'permitted'.

You need

    SendEnv LANG LC_*

in your client-side ssh config, and

    AcceptEnv LANG LC_*

in the remote sshd_config.

This requires OpenSSH 3.9 or later.

